OL,3,CWidow describes 'insulting' Post
OL,4,COffice payout offer days after
OL,5,Chusband's death
OL,7,FJanet Walters, the widow of former
OL,8,Fsubpostmaster Terry Walters, has
OL,9,Fcalled on the government to speed up
OL,10,Fcompensation for people caught up in
OL,11,Fthe Horizon IT Scandal.
OL,13,FThe widow of a former subpostmaster
OL,14,Fwho was caught up in the Horizon
OL,15,FScandal has described an offer of
OL,16,Fcompensation letter days after his
OL,17,Fdeath as an "insulting slap in the
OL,18,Fface."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
