OL,3,CWidow describes 'insulting' Post
OL,4,COffice payout offer days after
OL,5,Chusband's death
OL,7,FTerry Walters was one of hundreds of
OL,8,FPost Office workers who had their
OL,9,Fcontracts terminated due to a faulty
OL,10,FIT software which saw many people
OL,11,Fwrongly convicted of theft, fraud and
OL,12,Ffalse accounting based wrong data.
OL,14,FThe 76-year-old, who died in February
OL,15,F2025 after years of ill health, lost
OL,16,Fhis branch in Hockley, Stockport, over
OL,17,Fa shortfall of thousands of pounds,
OL,18,Fblamed on him but caused by the
OL,19,Fsoftware system developed by Fujitsu.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
