OL,3,CWidow describes 'insulting' Post
OL,4,COffice payout offer days after
OL,5,Chusband's death
OL,7,FSpeaking to Good Morning Britain, his
OL,8,Fwife Janet said the couple endured "17
OL,9,Fyears of misery" caused by one of the
OL,10,F"greatest miscarriages of justice in
OL,11,FBritish history."
OL,13,FTo make matters worse, her husband
OL,14,Fdied without receiving all the money
OL,15,Fhe was owed. She received the letter
OL,16,Fof compensation in the post just days
OL,17,Fafter his passing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
