OL,3,CWidow describes 'insulting' Post
OL,4,COffice payout offer days after
OL,5,Chusband's death
OL,7,FShe said: "My husband had struggled
OL,8,Fwith ill health for years. He had been
OL,9,Fupset by what we'd been through with
OL,10,Fthe Post Office. Then to have a letter
OL,11,Flike that come as though it was some
OL,12,Fkind of joke. I was flabbergasted."
OL,14,FThe government says it has doubled the
OL,15,Famount of payments made to former sub-
OL,16,Fpostmasters and are "making offers to
OL,17,F89.6% of claimants within 40 working
OL,18,Fdays."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
