OL,7,FLess than two years after taking over
OL,8,Fthe Post Office branch, Terry was
OL,9,Fsuspended for alleged shortfalls and
OL,10,Fhis contract was terminated the
OL,11,Ffollowing year.
OL,13,FHe and Janet had to sell their home
OL,14,Fand have been living in rented
OL,15,Faccommodation ever since.
OL,17,FMr Walters submitted a claim for full
OL,18,Ffinancial redress more than a year ago.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
