OL,3,CWidow describes 'insulting' Post
OL,4,COffice payout offer days after
OL,5,Chusband's death
OL,7,FJanet said: "They wanted a report
OL,8,Fabout his stroke which took months to
OL,9,Fcome back. Then my solicitor kept
OL,10,Fgoing back to them and asking if we
OL,11,Fwere going to have an offer. No offer
OL,12,Fcame.
OL,14,F"Christmas came and no offer. Then
OL,15,Feventually we got the offer in
OL,16,FFebruary, only days after Terry had
OL,17,Fpassed away which was upsetting as he
OL,18,Fwouldn't have accepted it.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
