OL,3,CWidow describes 'insulting' Post
OL,4,COffice payout offer days after
OL,5,Chusband's death
OL,7,F"I'm not going to accept it, it's an
OL,8,Finsult. I was annoyed. I was very
OL,9,Fannoyed. I'd like to ask the
OL,10,FGovernment why its taken so long? It's
OL,11,Fa miscarriage of justice which they
OL,12,Fshould have honoured.
OL,14,F"They are messing me about now with
OL,15,Foffers, it shouldn't be about offers
OL,16,Fit should be about putting us back
OL,17,Fwhere we were with our money. They
OL,18,Ftook that money from us."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
