OL,7,FTerry is one of a growing number of
OL,8,Fformer sub-postmasters and sub-
OL,9,Fpostmistresses to die amid delays to
OL,10,Fthe compensation.
OL,12,FJanet added: "When we got the letter
OL,13,Fit was like a slap in the face. The
OL,14,FGovernment should do the honourable
OL,15,Fthing and pay it in full because it
OL,16,Fwas our own money, most of it."
OL,18,FA statement from the Government says:
OL,19,F"We are sorry to hear about Terry's
OL,20,Fdeath and our thoughts are with Janet.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
